                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320216-205-off1154 t18320216-205-cd1155"></join>, 1 counterpane. value 1s.; 2 blankets, value 2s.; 2 sheets, value 2s.; 2 pillows, value 2s.; 1 bolster, value 2s.; 2 pillow-cases, value 6d.; 1 bolster-case, value 6d.; 1 swing looking-glass, value 2s.; 4 pieces of earthenware, value 2s.; 2 flat-irons, value 8d.; 1 saucepan and cover, value 2s., and 1 tea-kettle, value 1s.
