            . I am the wife of John Dale - he lives in <placeName id="t18320216-205-crimeloc1156">High-street, Portland-town</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320216-205-crimeloc1156" type="placeName" value="High-street, Portland-town"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320216-205-crimeloc1156" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320216-205-off1154 t18320216-205-crimeloc1156"></join>; the prisoners had a furnished room of mine for four months. On the 22nd of January I went into the room, and missed these articles; all the bed-clothes were gone - when I asked the male prisoner to let me look at the bed he said, "No, Mrs. Dale, there is something gone, but we will make it all right on Tuesday" - I insisted on having the duplicates, and he took them from his wife, and gave them to me; I gave them to the officer, but he was not bound over.</p>
               <p>
